{"tid":1982672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）集運比人呃 如果有佢香港同美國地址可以點做","createTime":"2020-04-21T10:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:28:59.000Z","uid":213049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d02031a7ebd8c6062b56e42d3b2119039956a71","tid":1982672,"uid":213049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lovehoneybeebee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flovehoneybeebee%2F&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=b5eab276\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lovehoneybeebee/</a><br />\n啲嘢2月買 開頭佢都有覆我，後來就直接不回覆訊息，一直拖咗兩個幾月 啱啱仲是旦比個順豐號碼我就block咗我<br />\n雖然有佢門市 但應該要點做 唔想靠香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U96sYfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU96sYfe.jpg&h=185daa8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問有佢門市同美國嗰面地址有冇啲咩可以做? <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88sowAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88sowAo.jpg&h=d404da50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1eddbd5aa5571215c877628f189c0eba001661","tid":1982672,"uid":276989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"呢d私人集運風險自負啦"},{"pid":"6ce9b82c98bfdbc434f6e5d9a1419fbc81a4cb1f","tid":1982672,"uid":213049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d1eddbd5aa5571215c877628f189c0eba001661","tid":1982672,"uid":276989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"呢d私人集運風險自負啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"佢好似有公司登記，又有門市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣, 請入數到以下戶口,<br />\n匯豐銀行: 652-591975-838 <br />\n中國銀行: 012-553-0-004826-7 <br />\n轉數快(FPS)電話: 55019833<br />\n戶口名稱: LHBB COMPANY LIMITED<br />\n<br />\n麻煩你whatsapp／ email／facebook入數紙俾我地, 會馬上為你訂購, 大概3-4星期到港, 可於門市自取, 港鐵尖沙咀, 旺角, 香港大學, 上環, 中環, 金鐘, 灣仔, 銅鑼灣, 或鰂魚涌站交收(額外收費全免), 如順豐站自取$30, 亦可安排速遞費到付~<br />\n   <br />\n取貨期為我地發出取貨通知後一年內, 逾時將作棄單論, 所訂之貨品及訂金將不獲退還, 如單一貨品斷貨, 我地會全數退回該單一貨品嘅款項~<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp: (HK) 55019833<br />\n(USA) +14082031592<br />\n<br />\n E-mail: lovehoneybeebee@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\nAddress: <br />\n石塘咀522-530皇后大道西再發大廈地下6號鋪 (港鐵香港大學站B2出口) (星期二/三/五15:30-19:00, 星期六15:30-18:30)"},{"pid":"f0983cd436e99710c9545f6475741227a250358e","tid":1982672,"uid":213049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"除咗報警仲有冇巴打有其他辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c25110de7e44b8a7c47f3b86d2eadfd410d6c8e","tid":1982672,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"報比美國稅局"},{"pid":"4e3b8eb7ed6d9ae2c3a5f29b4a9865f4a23e678d","tid":1982672,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"不過唔好話佢知你報左"},{"pid":"a51a7cbe3671cd057eb21b7659820d0c60cf5535","tid":1982672,"uid":213049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b8eb7ed6d9ae2c3a5f29b4a9865f4a23e678d","tid":1982672,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"不過唔好話佢知你報左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51245f0b4ec2590a7b3e391b71511698792bd95","tid":1982672,"uid":213049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b8eb7ed6d9ae2c3a5f29b4a9865f4a23e678d","tid":1982672,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"不過唔好話佢知你報左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":